         <OBJECT_CONTRACT ITEM="1">
            <TITLE>
               <P>Certified Internal Auditor Training</P>
            </TITLE>
            <REFERENCE_NUMBER>388587</REFERENCE_NUMBER>
            <CPV_MAIN>
               <CPV_CODE CODE="80500000"/>
            </CPV_MAIN>
            <SHORT_DESCR>
               <P>The Scottish Government (SG) Internal Audit Directorate (IAD) wishes to commission a contractor to provide Certified Internal Auditor (CIA) training in Edinburgh, to enable an initial cohort of around 24 internal auditors the opportunity to achieve relevant professional accreditation and competence. This will be a single supplier, multiple year framework agreement, with the possibility of extension should an additional cohort of trainees be required. The additional cohort would likely be around 12 further students.</P>
            </SHORT_DESCR>
            <NO_LOT_DIVISION/>
            <OBJECT_DESCR ITEM="1">
               <CPV_ADDITIONAL>
                  <CPV_CODE CODE="80500000"/>
               </CPV_ADDITIONAL>
